trans-unit.source: 1. Make sure the company you are importing to does not already contain customers, vendors, or items, if you want to import these entities.
trans-unit.target: 1. Kontrollér, at den virksomhed, du importerer til, ikke allerede indeholder debitorer, kreditorer eller varer, hvis du vil importere disse enheder.
trans-unit.note: Codeunit C5 Wizard Integration - NamedType Instructions1Txt

trans-unit.source: 2. Open Microsoft Dynamics C5 2008, and export your database. (General > Setup > Administration > Multi > Export Database).
trans-unit.target: 2. Åbn Microsoft Dynamics C5 2008, og eksportér databasen. (Generelt > Opsætning > Administration > Flere > Eksportér databasen).
trans-unit.note: Codeunit C5 Wizard Integration - NamedType Instructions2Txt

trans-unit.source: 3. Send the export folder to a compressed (zipped) folder.
trans-unit.target: 3. Send mappen til eksport til en komprimeret (zippet) mappe.
trans-unit.note: Codeunit C5 Wizard Integration - NamedType Instructions3Txt

trans-unit.source: 4. Return to this assisted setup guide, choose Next, and then import the zipped folder.
trans-unit.target: 4. Gå tilbage til guiden for assisteret opsætning, vælg Næste, og importér derefter den zippede mappe.
trans-unit.note: Codeunit C5 Wizard Integration - NamedType Instructions4Txt

trans-unit.target: Du kan kontrollere status for dataoverførslen ved at gå til siden %1.
